Super Formula is a very competitive Japanese single-seater series that is the closest in terms of car performance to F1. Here's how the cars compare

Share Tweet Email Whatsapp

Here are Car Throttle, we like to take a look at how different forms of motorsport compare. From LMP1 vs LMP2 in the FIA WEC to what the differences are between a WRC machine and its road-going counterpart. We’ve already looked at how F1 cars compare to GP2
